&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Artist Aaron Koblin takes vast amounts of data &amp;ndash; and at times vast numbers of people &amp;ndash; and weaves them into stunning visualizations. From elegant lines tracing airline flights to landscapes of cell phone data, from a Johnny Cash video assembled from crowd-sourced drawings to the &amp;ldquo;Wilderness Downtown&amp;rdquo; video that customizes for the user, his works brilliantly explore how modern technology can make us more human.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
