&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;notebook-screenshot&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.uistencils.com/products/ipad-dry-erase-white-board&#34;&gt;&lt;img id=&#39;bluga-thumbnail-2476&#39; class=&#39;bluga-thumbnail large&#39; src=&#39;http://media.konigi.com/bluga/
