wt4bc4a180be46d_large.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;If I were an Axure user, this is what I would be using. Version 2 of Loren Baxter&amp;rsquo;s of the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.acleandesign.com/2010/04/axure-better-defaults-library-v2/&#34;&gt;Better Defaults library&lt;/a&gt; has been expanded to sixty five (or so) interactive and cleanly styled widgets. Use it in place of the standard widget set.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

