&lt;p&gt;I love how the cats run off the side of the canvas. Oh, and how no one in that meeting is paying attention... Awesome.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://markandrewgoetz.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/tufte-wallpaper.png&#34;&gt;http://markandrewgoetz.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/tufte-wallpaper.png&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;notebook-image&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4024/4421064984_e1f31f3954_o.png&#34; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Panic got inspiration from &lt;a href=&#34;http://culturedcode.com/status/&#34;&gt;Cultured Code&amp;rsquo;s Development Status Board&lt;/a&gt; and crafted their own &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.panic.com/blog/2010/03/the-panic-status-board/&#34;&gt;dashboard/status board&lt;/a&gt;, displayed in a flat screen TV. &lt;/p&gt;
