wt4a561c2a3aa65.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://helveticons.ch/&#34;&gt;Helveticons&lt;/a&gt; are royalty-free vector icons, glyphs and symbols based on the Helvetica Bold typeface. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

