wt4a0384ec3f448_0.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;On Made By Many, Isaac Pinnock &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.madebymany.co.uk/the-future-of-wireframes-00991&#34;&gt;looks back at his 10 year history using wireframes&lt;/a&gt; and their evolution in IA practice from time consuming deliverable in functional specifications, to disposable artifacts of the design process. The notion that highly visual wireframes should be part of the design process resonates with me. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

