&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;notebook-screenshot&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.flickr.com/groups/prettysketchy/&#34;&gt;&lt;img id=&#39;bluga-thumbnail-1590&#39; class=&#39;bluga-thumbnail large&#39; src=&#39;http://media.konigi.com/bluga/
wt4a003a9936a2c.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jason Santa Maria started a sketchbook group on flickr. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sketchbooks are not about being a good artist, they’re about being a good thinker. In the spirit of awareness, I’ve set up a Flickr group for this very purpose. Post one, and only one, spread/page from your sketchbook. It’s always fun to see how everyone else’s mind works.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Read more about it in Jason&amp;rsquo;s post &lt;a href=&#34;http://jasonsantamaria.com/articles/pretty-sketchy/&#34;&gt;Pretty Sketchy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.flickr.com/groups/prettysketchy/&#34;&gt;http://www.flickr.com/groups/prettysketchy/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;notebook-screenshot&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://shop.konigi.com/paper-products?q=store/paper-products&#34;&gt;&lt;img id=&#39;bluga-thumbnail-1589&#39; class=&#39;bluga-thumbnail large&#39; src=&#39;http://media.konigi.com/bluga/
wt49fb0a11193d7.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&#34;http://shop.konigi.com/paper-products?q=store/paper-products&#34;&gt;Wireframe and Storyboard notepads&lt;/a&gt; have been reprinted and are now selling exclusively via Amazon.com. The good news is, now that you ordered via Amazon, your order may qualify for Free Super Saver Shipping, and may be combined with other Amazon purchases in your cart. So if you spend $25 at Amazon, even by combining your purchase with other qualified products fulfilled via Amazon, your shipping will be free. Yay, you!&lt;/p&gt;
