wt4999572a9af98.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Smart Experience has posted &lt;a href=&#34;http://smartexperience.org/sp/ixd-skills-carousels/&#34;&gt;a 5 minute video&lt;/a&gt; showing different kinds of carousels in action and teaches you the three key design criteria you need to know to create your own. Excellent stuff and the best discussion of why carousels are effective, and a thorough review of the different kinds of carousels you might use. Check it for free now. This micro-seminar goes on sale soon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

