&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://sixrevisions.com/web_design/20-websites-with-beautiful-typography/&#34;&gt;http://sixrevisions.com/web_design/20-websites-with-beautiful-typography/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

