&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;notebook-screenshot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/notebook/sketch-iterations.jpg&#34; class=&#34;notebook-image&#34; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;These are just more illustrations of the process I&amp;rsquo;ve been using for design iterations. When I have the Konigi notebook available, I&amp;rsquo;ll be doing some screencasts to describe this process in detail, and why I felt the need to make these graph paper notebooks and pads.&lt;/p&gt;
