&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;notebook-screenshot&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dubberly.com/articles/how-do-you-design.html&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://media.konigi.com/notebook/how-do-you-design-book.jpg&#34; class=&#34;notebook-image&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hugh Dubberly has released a free &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dubberly.com/articles/how-do-you-design.html&#34;&gt;E Book on design and development models&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
