&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;notebook-screenshot&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.crowdscience.com/&#34;&gt;&lt;img id=&#39;bluga-thumbnail-1391&#39; class=&#39;bluga-thumbnail large&#39; src=&#39;http://media.konigi.com/bluga/
wt490779853e17f.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.crowdscience.com/&#34;&gt;Crowd Science&lt;/a&gt; is a new comer among user research services that allow you to prompt small sets of users to participate in questionnaires while they&amp;rsquo;re browsing your site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Crowd Science Demographics is a new analytics service that builds detailed reports on the demographics and attitudes of website audiences. By surveying a small number visitors with carefully constructed questionnaires, Crowd Science Demographics is able to build comprehensive audience profiles that give publishers a deep understanding of their audience. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

