wt4821afabbaa37.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Christian Behrens&amp;rsquo; &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.niceone.org/infodesignpatterns/index.php5#/home.php5&#34;&gt;information design pattern repository&lt;/a&gt; collects solutions for &amp;ldquo;&amp;hellip;the display, behavior, and user interaction of complex infographics. The collection is available in the form of a 200-page book that additionally includes a profound historical record of information design as well as an introduction inthe research field of design patterns.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

