&lt;p&gt;Smashing Magazine has collected a series of pictures &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.smashingmagazine.com/2008/04/21/celebration-of-vintage-and-retro-design/&#34;&gt;celebrating vintage and retro desigtn&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#8212;ads, illustrations, book covers, pins and posters from 1920-1980s or inspired by that period. &lt;/p&gt;


