wt47f7adb8e2108.jpg&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.shouldredesign.com/&#34;&gt;Should Redesign&lt;/a&gt; is a new design gallery that displays a screenshot of a site and asks users to vote on whether or not they should be redesigned.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

